  "screens": [
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s031",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "来看一个具体的例子。",
        "我们有一个数据集，记录了一些人的信息以及他们是否拥有电脑。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s032",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "现在来了一个新记录 X：",
        "年龄<30，收入中等，是学生，信用评级差。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s033",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "这个记录在数据集中不存在。",
        "所以无法直接知道它是否拥有电脑。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s034",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "我们用朴素贝叶斯来算。",
        "先算 P(拥有电脑) = 9/14，P(没有电脑) = 5/14。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "categorical_attribute"
      ],
      "id": "s035",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "categorical_attribute"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "然后，对于 <term id=\"categorical_attribute\">类别型属性</term>，比如年龄，",
        "我们直接数：在拥有电脑的人中，年龄<30 的有 2 个，所以概率是 2/9。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s036",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "类似地，收入中等：4/9；是学生：6/9；信用差：6/9。",
        "把它们乘起来：P(X|拥有电脑) = (2/9)*(4/9)*(6/9)*(6/9) ≈ 0.044"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s037",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "再算 P(X|没有电脑) ≈ 0.019。",
        "然后比较：P(X|拥有电脑)*P(拥有电脑) 和 P(X|没有电脑)*P(没有电脑)。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s038",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "结果是 0.028 > 0.007。",
        "所以，X 被分类为“拥有电脑”。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "numerical_attribute"
      ],
      "id": "s039",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "numerical_attribute"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "那如果属性是数值型的呢？比如“收入”是 120K。",
        "我们不能简单地数个数了。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s040",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "一种方法是离散化：把收入分成几个区间。",
        "但结果对区间的划分方式很敏感。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "probability_density_estimation"
      ],
      "id": "s041",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "probability_density_estimation"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "更好的方法是 <term id=\"probability_density_estimation\">概率密度估计</term>。",
        "假设数值属性服从正态分布，用数据估计均值和方差。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "formula": {
